text: Good pizza at a very good price. Much cheaper (if you get coupons or specials) than the other pizza places in the area. I got 2 large (more like medium) with 2 toppings for under$20.

text: I love the food here but there delivery sucks. They say when I order 20-30 minutes, and then take an hour or even longer. I tried picking up in the store once and they ended up sending my order out for delivery and had to bring it back. I don't think I'm gonna eat here anymore.
